Some big news from the @ONS about #COVID19 in Wales.🏴󠁧󠁢󠁷󠁬󠁳󠁿

An estimated 61% of adults had coronavirus antibodies in the week ending 11th April... which means they've been vaccinated or had the virus.🦠

This graph shows the #Vaccine effect and the numbers of peopel building defence: https://t.co/J6yKiRPNsv
